    "Ophth Part 2 mock examination.",
    "PaLM 2 did not attain pass-worthy performance or match expert ophthalmologists' scores but was within the spread of trainee doctors' performance.",
    "LLMs are approaching human expert-level knowledge and reasoning in ophthalmology, and significantly exceed the ability of non-specialist clinicians (represented here by unspecialised junior doctors) to answer ophthalmology questions."
